data.description: AMAZING OPPORTUNITY TO ASSUME THE SELLER'S LOAN AT 6.1%!!! WATERFRONT! COMMUNITY ACCESS TO LAKE HARRIS!  Enjoy the rare opportunity to live in this incredible subdivision!  You will have plenty of space to create the home of your dreams with a floor plan that works well for all. Enjoy the galley GOURMET kitchen with gas cooking and all appliances included!  The master bedroom features an en-suite bath. The 2nd and 3rd bedrooms each have ample closet space. You will love your oversized screened-in lanai looking out onto the pond - create your own outdoor oasis!  Enjoy your pond with a view with your morning coffee or afternoon tea! The Springs Park Area is a private residential community on the shores of Lake Harris and features incredible amenities including a community pool and clubhouse, community fishing pier, and recreational activities. Conveniently located in downtown Yalaha - lots of shopping, dining, and recreational choices are within minutes of the property! This is a must-see neighborhood and property just waiting for you to make it your own. Come see all this home has to offer!
